thread.title: Beydon Sherwood

author: Beydon Sherwood
title: Beydon Sherwood
text: When we arrived, the lady from Budget told us all our options with insuring the car, we however, had already insured though some other company, that they offer through the Advertising Agent. It would be good if we could know about it beforehand. We were offered an upgrade to a bigger vehicle. The vehicle kept notifying me that it needed an oil change other than that,everything worked, and it was a good vehicle with no issues what so ever. Thank you.
